{"word":"H79 - אָבַק - ʼâbaq - aw-bak' - Wrestle","slug":"H79","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אָבַק</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʼâbaq"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>aw-bak'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Wrestle"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D0;&#x05D1;&#x05E7; - 'a&#x0302;baq</b> - <i>aw-bak'</i><p/>A primitive root; probably to <i>float</i> away (as vapor), but used only as denominative from <a href=\"#/H80\">H80</a>; to <i>bedust</i>, that is, <i>grapple: - </i>wrestle."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H80\">H80</a>, <a href=\"#/H81\">H81</a>"}]}